import React, { Component } from 'react';

import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Route,
  Redirect
} from "react-router-dom";
import { NavBar } from '../components'
import protectedRoute from '../pages/Login/protectedRoute'
import { Login, Admin, OrdersHistory, Home, ManageUsers, Register } from '../pages'

   
class App extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
     
      <Router>
        <Route exact path="/">
          <Login />
        </Route>

        <protectedRoute exact path="/home">
        <NavBar> 
        </NavBar>
          <Home />
        </protectedRoute>
        
{/*       
        <protectedRoute exact path="/admin">
        <NavBar> 
        </NavBar>
          <Admin path="../pages" />
        </protectedRoute>
        
        <protectedRoute exact path="/admin/register">
        <NavBar> 
        </NavBar>
          <Register path="../pages" />
        </protectedRoute>

        <protectedRoute exact path="/admin/ManageUsers">
        <NavBar> 
        </NavBar>
          <ManageUsers path="../pages" />
        </protectedRoute>
        <protectedRoute exact path="/admin/ordershistory">
        <NavBar> 
        </NavBar>
          <OrdersHistory path="../pages" />
        </protectedRoute> */}

      </Router>
    )
  }
}
export default App
